{"id":"8a70bc2a340bc995d16f8fc783267cd5ff2134e7fabe566b8201d3e7cb8c314e","item_id":"3f337fc74d:0","text":"要了解 PxrSurface 的所有细节及其可分层参数，请访问"}
{"id":"9cced1a6fc04e8f446eb25e011003ae009636abd221e82157bd920a5072fce7c","item_id":"3f337fc74d:1","text":"Pixar Surface Materials"}
{"id":"7d947ed3fefc5e80f1e1dc929e66fc1614ea9d00dc06fa51b2c10e1306a184b8","item_id":"3f337fc74d:3","text":"创建简单分层材质最容易的方法是打开 RenderMan 菜单，选择 Create Material（创建材质），然后选择 Pxr Layered Surface。这里会在 MAT 面板中创建并连接一个分层材质。"}
{"id":"1543d66e96e19d476bc59f361ad04207a1a63a2a212195ca316427e5af664ea9","item_id":"3f337fc74d:4","text":"PxrLayer"}
{"id":"1543d66e96e19d476bc59f361ad04207a1a63a2a212195ca316427e5af664ea9","item_id":"3f337fc74d:8","text":"PxrLayer"}
{"id":"82ceee3619c9d5062c87c0d9bca31a38e883c259c68f4a7f0a7cefdec4ea1a9d","item_id":"3f337fc74d:5","text":"可以覆盖"}
{"id":"278b86b5926f2c73593d4f04b38e1ac76e47539cbb291bc68e1e22eba52834f1","item_id":"3f337fc74d:7","text":"中的参数，方法是使用"}
{"id":"f63eceaa72449cbbf047274551f8ca420f9fc029bb073edbcc3c8207f093ce42","item_id":"3f337fc74d:9","text":"选项。"}
{"id":"fea3747860ed5e9d4ea9a4d102406eee07a559825d2b4f58add2a29fe78d0463","item_id":"3f337fc74d:10","text":"在这个示例中，我们在 PxrSurface 中设置绿色 diffuse color（漫反射颜色）。然后在其上方叠加一个带有青色 diffuse color 的 PxrLayer 节点。请注意，一种颜色会覆盖另一种颜色，因此需要调整 Mixer node。"}
{"id":"d55cac660677a6bc8a895d495a9653e024951269fb09b3d728d3faae3b5b8605","item_id":"3f337fc74d:11","text":"PxrLayer Mixer"}
{"id":"d7ccf34b32d8c32f1c8460ed20c3aa3045f656da223a565886ad50d4fe29e99f","item_id":"3f337fc74d:12","text":"可以使用"}
{"id":"244f48b3e1671c5e156f17919f1e85fb70be4f1606f82ff6821b6bf83ff4c6be","item_id":"3f337fc74d:13","text":"PxrLayerMixer"}
{"id":"efeb83a5a66b3e16488f00189ec0fd01a287790bec0ad39b9f2b848e1a0e96d0","item_id":"3f337fc74d:14","text":" 来组合 layers（层）。Mixer 用于决定通过 mask 在哪里以及如何混合各个 layer。下面，patterns 会连接到 Mixer 中的 Mask。"}
{"id":"02705dbe9eb73e733cc7173fcf3dcbfb0bbe3da084a7cb31082e8a5969faca8c","item_id":"3f337fc74d:15","text":"可以对 specular（镜面）、iridescence（虹彩）和其他 illumination lobes（照明波瓣）进行分层。"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "3f337fc74d:2", "text": "。"}
{"id": "8608905e6533fb79c29dcbee9e54642763cc7988fd456046ba16656c6564e8fd", "item_id": "3f337fc74d:6", "text": "PxrSurface"}
